<p>The businesses that invest in <a href="/glossary/local-pack/">local SEO</a> signals today are building the foundation for agentic commerce visibility tomorrow.</p>
<p>This is not speculation. Google already uses GBP data in AI Mode responses for local queries. When AI agents fully integrate with local discovery, the businesses with the strongest local SEO signals will dominate agent-based recommendations. The ones with incomplete profiles will be invisible.</p>
